{"type":"message","id":"bc2d71c8","parentId":"5fa40afb","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:22:41.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to read a local API documentation file and fill it with real data from their running plugin service. Let me first read the file to understand what needs to be filled in.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e780b83d08a24bf29e905aa8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\code\\request-analyzer\\API_DOC.zh-CN.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773159758159}}
{"type":"message","id":"48a2a8ec","parentId":"bc2d71c8","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:22:41.432Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e780b83d08a24bf29e905aa8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ContextScope HTTP API 接口文档\n\nBase URL（默认）：`http://127.0.0.1:18789`\n\n插件路径前缀：\n- Dashboard：`/plugins/contextscope`\n- API：`/plugins/contextscope/api/*`\n\n示例数据（本机联调）：\n- `runId`: `fad76360-a689-4d85-8371-605388ee922e`\n- `sessionId`: `ctxscope-test`\n\n## 1) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/stats\n\n返回总体统计、存储统计与前端展示配置。\n\nQuery 参数：无\n\n响应（示例，截取）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"totalRequests\": 40,\n    \"todayRequests\": 40,\n    \"weekRequests\": 40,\n    \"averageTokens\": 0,\n    \"totalCost\": 0,\n    \"byProvider\": { \"bailian\": 32, \"anthropic\": 8 },\n    \"byModel\": { \"qwen3.5-plus\": 32, \"claude-opus-4-6\": 8 }\n  },\n  \"storage\": {\n    \"totalRequests\": 40,\n    \"todayRequests\": 40,\n    \"weekRequests\": 40,\n    \"storageSize\": \"…\",\n    \"oldestRequest\": 1773081035652,\n    \"newestRequest\": 1773158170807\n  },\n  \"config\": {\n    \"theme\": \"dark\",\n    \"autoRefresh\": true,\n    \"refreshInterval\": 5000\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 2) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/requests\n\n按过滤条件返回 LLM 请求/响应事件列表（同一个 `runId` 可能会有多条 input/output）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `sessionId`（可选）\n- `runId`（可选）\n- `provider`（可选）\n- `model`（可选）\n- `startTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `endTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应结构：\n- `requests`: `RequestData[]`\n- `total`: 当前返回条数（注意不是全量总数）\n- `filters`: 实际生效的过滤条件（含默认值）\n\n响应（示例，按 runId 查询，截取）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"requests\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 39,\n      \"type\": \"output\",\n      \"runId\": \"fad76360-a689-4d85-8371-605388ee922e\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"ctxscope-test\",\n      \"provider\": \"anthropic\",\n      \"model\": \"claude-opus-4-6\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773158172060,\n      \"assistantTexts\": [\"HTTP 403 forbidden: Request not allowed\"],\n      \"usage\": { \"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0 }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 40,\n      \"type\": \"input\",\n      \"runId\": \"fad76360-a689-4d85-8371-605388ee922e\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"ctxscope-test\",\n      \"provider\": \"anthropic\",\n      \"model\": \"claude-opus-4-6\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773158170807,\n      \"prompt\": \"[Tue 2026-03-10 23:56 GMT+8] ContextScope gateway ping 2\",\n      \"systemPrompt\": \"…\",\n      \"historyMessages\": []\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 2,\n  \"filters\": {\n    \"runId\": \"fad76360-a689-4d85-8371-605388ee922e\",\n    \"limit\": 10,\n    \"offset\": 0\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 3) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/analysis\n\n按 `runId` 返回聚合分析结果（token breakdown、timeline、insights 等）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n\n错误：\n- `400`: 缺少 `runId`\n- `404`: 找不到对应 `runId`\n\n响应（示例，截取）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"runId\": \"fad76360-a689-4d85-8371-605388ee922e\",\n  \"sessionId\": \"ctxscope-test\",\n  \"provider\": \"anthropic\",\n  \"model\": \"claude-opus-4-6\",\n  \"timestamp\": 1773158170807,\n  \"tokenBreakdown\": { \"labels\": [\"…\"], \"values\": [6856, 256, 14, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"total\": 7126 },\n  \"timeline\": {\n    \"points\": [\n      { \"timestamp\": 1773158170807, \"tokens\": 6870, \"messages\": 1, \"utilization\": 0.8386, \"summaryApplied\": true },\n      { \"timestamp\": 1773158172060, \"tokens\": 6870, \"messages\": 2, \"utilization\": 0.8386, \"summaryApplied\": true }\n    ],\n    \"contextWindow\": 8192\n  },\n  \"insights\": [{ \"type\": \"optimization\", \"title\": \"…\", \"severity\": \"medium\" }]\n}\n```\n\n## 4) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/session\n\n按 `sessionId` 返回会话级统计与分析。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `sessionId`（必填）\n\n错误：\n- `400`: 缺少 `sessionId`\n- `404`: 找不到会话分析\n\n## 5) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/links\n\n返回主/子任务（subagent）关联边列表（spawn/send/ended）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `parentRunId`（可选）\n- `childRunId`（可选）\n- `parentSessionId`（可选）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应结构：\n- `links`: `SubagentLinkData[]`\n- `total`: 当前返回条数\n- `filters`\n\n## 6) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/tool-calls\n\n返回工具调用 span 列表（来自 `after_tool_call` 采集）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（可选）\n- `sessionId`（可选）\n- `toolName`（可选）\n- `startTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `endTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应（示例：该 run 未触发 tool call，因此为空）：\n\n```json\n{ \"toolCalls\": [], \"total\": 0, \"filters\": { \"runId\": \"fad76360-a689-4d85-8371-605388ee922e\", \"limit\": 5, \"offset\": 0 } }\n```\n\n## 7) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/export\n\n导出请求事件数据。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `format`（可选，`json` | `csv`，默认 `json`）\n- `startTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `endTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `provider`（可选）\n- `model`（可选）\n\n响应：\n- `format=json`: `application/json`，内容为 `RequestData[]`\n- `format=csv`: `text/csv`\n\n## 8) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/timeline/detail\n\n返回某个 timeline point 的上下文快照。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n- `timestamp`（必填，毫秒时间戳；通常取自 `/api/analysis` 的 `timeline.points[].timestamp`）\n\n响应（示例）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": 1773158170807,\n  \"tokens\": 0,\n  \"messages\": 1,\n  \"utilization\": 0,\n  \"summaryApplied\": false,\n  \"contextSnapshot\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"fad76360-a689-4d85-8371-605388ee922e\",\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"[Tue 2026-03-10 23:56 GMT+8] ContextScope gateway ping 2\",\n      \"tokens\": 0,\n      \"timestamp\": 1773158170807,\n      \"type\": \"input\",\n      \"status\": \"success\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 9) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/timeline/compare\n\n对比两个 timeline point 的差异。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n- `timestamp1`（必填）\n- `timestamp2`（必填）\n\n响应（示例）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp1\": 1773158172060,\n  \"timestamp2\": 1773158172060,\n  \"messagesDelta\": 0,\n  \"tokensDelta\": 0,\n  \"utilizationDelta\": 10,\n  \"addedMessages\": [],\n  \"removedMessages\": []\n}\n```\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773159761304}}
