{"type":"message","id":"deab51fe","parentId":"0b5e1bc7","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:23:51.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I now have enough real data from the running service to update the API documentation. Let me write the updated file with actual data from the plugin service.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the real data. Let me update the API documentation file with actual data from the running service:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_05c6f4b986b6421f8615e249","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"D:\\code\\request-analyzer\\API_DOC.zh-CN.md","content":"# ContextScope HTTP API 接口文档\n\nBase URL（默认）：`http://127.0.0.1:18789`\n\n插件路径前缀：\n- Dashboard：`/plugins/contextscope`\n- API：`/plugins/contextscope/api/*`\n\n示例数据（本机联调，实时数据）：\n- `runId`: `0c28e5e1-581e-42df-ad47-2ba40aa1c8c2`\n- `sessionId`: `2accf470-a410-405c-ad91-2d1cb497176d`\n\n## 1) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/stats\n\n返回总体统计、存储统计与前端展示配置。\n\nQuery 参数：无\n\n响应（实时数据）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"totalRequests\": 45,\n    \"todayRequests\": 5,\n    \"weekRequests\": 45,\n    \"averageTokens\": 0,\n    \"totalCost\": 0,\n    \"byProvider\": { \"bailian\": 37, \"openrouter\": 2, \"anthropic\": 6 },\n    \"byModel\": { \"qwen3.5-plus\": 37, \"anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet\": 2, \"claude-opus-4-6\": 6 },\n    \"hourlyDistribution\": [5, 0, 6, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 18, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 10]\n  },\n  \"storage\": {\n    \"totalRequests\": 45,\n    \"todayRequests\": 5,\n    \"weekRequests\": 45,\n    \"storageSize\": \"13.1 MB\",\n    \"oldestRequest\": 1773081035652,\n    \"newestRequest\": 1773159767282\n  },\n  \"config\": {\n    \"theme\": \"dark\",\n    \"autoRefresh\": true,\n    \"refreshInterval\": 5000\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 2) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/requests\n\n按过滤条件返回 LLM 请求/响应事件列表（同一个 `runId` 可能会有多条 input/output）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `sessionId`（可选）\n- `runId`（可选）\n- `provider`（可选）\n- `model`（可选）\n- `startTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `endTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应结构：\n- `requests`: `RequestData[]`\n- `total`: 当前返回条数（注意不是全量总数）\n- `filters`: 实际生效的过滤条件（含默认值）\n\n响应（实时数据，limit=5）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"requests\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"input\",\n      \"runId\": \"0c28e5e1-581e-42df-ad47-2ba40aa1c8c2\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"2accf470-a410-405c-ad91-2d1cb497176d\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"provider\": \"bailian\",\n      \"model\": \"qwen3.5-plus\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773159758047,\n      \"prompt\": \"[Wed 2026-03-11 00:22 GMT+8] 你本地有个 D:\\\\code\\\\request-analyzer\\\\API_DOC.zh-CN.md...\",\n      \"systemPrompt\": \"...\",\n      \"historyMessages\": [],\n      \"imagesCount\": 0,\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 45\n    },\n    {\n      \"type\": \"output\",\n      \"runId\": \"4a2ae89b-3d65-4466-8ed1-11c7c01e394e\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"ctxscope-success\",\n      \"provider\": \"bailian\",\n      \"model\": \"qwen3.5-plus\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773158975235,\n      \"assistantTexts\": [\"ok\"],\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 44\n    },\n    {\n      \"type\": \"input\",\n      \"runId\": \"4a2ae89b-3d65-4466-8ed1-11c7c01e394e\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"ctxscope-success\",\n      \"provider\": \"bailian\",\n      \"model\": \"qwen3.5-plus\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773158963814,\n      \"prompt\": \"[Wed 2026-03-11 00:09 GMT+8] 测试一下 ok\",\n      \"systemPrompt\": \"...\",\n      \"historyMessages\": [...],\n      \"imagesCount\": 0,\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 43\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"filters\": {\n    \"limit\": 5,\n    \"offset\": 0\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 3) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/analysis\n\n按 `runId` 返回聚合分析结果（token breakdown、timeline、insights 等）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n\n错误：\n- `400`: 缺少 `runId`\n- `404`: 找不到对应 `runId`\n\n响应（实时数据，runId=4a2ae89b-3d65-4466-8ed1-11c7c01e394e）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"runId\": \"4a2ae89b-3d65-4466-8ed1-11c7c01e394e\",\n  \"sessionId\": \"ctxscope-success\",\n  \"provider\": \"bailian\",\n  \"model\": \"qwen3.5-plus\",\n  \"timestamp\": 1773158963814,\n  \"tokenBreakdown\": {\n    \"labels\": [\"系统提示词\", \"用户消息内容\", \"历史消息\", \"工具响应\", \"图片描述\", \"元数据\", \"其他\"],\n    \"values\": [6852, 126, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0],\n    \"colors\": [\"#FF6384\", \"#36A2EB\", \"#FFCE56\", \"#4BC0C0\", \"#9966FF\", \"#FF9F40\", \"#C9CBCF\"],\n    \"total\": 6989\n  },\n  \"heatmap\": {\n    \"messages\": [\n      { \"id\": \"msg-0\", \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"...\", \"tokens\": 17, \"impact\": 98, \"timestamp\": 1773158774091 },\n      { \"id\": \"msg-1\", \"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"[]\", \"tokens\": 1, \"impact\": 96, \"timestamp\": 1773158774125 }\n    ],\n    \"maxImpact\": 98\n  },\n  \"timeline\": {\n    \"points\": [\n      { \"timestamp\": 1773158963814, \"tokens\": 6863, \"messages\": 1, \"utilization\": 0.209, \"summaryApplied\": false },\n      { \"timestamp\": 1773158975235, \"tokens\": 6863, \"messages\": 2, \"utilization\": 0.209, \"summaryApplied\": false }\n    ],\n    \"contextWindow\": 32768\n  },\n  \"dependencyGraph\": { \"nodes\": [], \"edges\": [] },\n  \"insights\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"optimization\",\n      \"title\": \"系统提示词占用过高\",\n      \"description\": \"系统提示词占用 98% 的 token，建议优化系统提示词长度\",\n      \"severity\": \"medium\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"topicClusters\": [\n    { \"topic\": \"text\", \"messageCount\": 1, \"percentage\": 50, \"keywords\": [\"text\"] },\n    { \"topic\": \"2026\", \"messageCount\": 1, \"percentage\": 50, \"keywords\": [\"2026\"] },\n    { \"topic\": \"type\", \"messageCount\": 1, \"percentage\": 50, \"keywords\": [\"type\"] }\n  ],\n  \"contextSimilarities\": [],\n  \"compressionSuggestions\": [\n    { \"type\": \"keep\", \"messageId\": \"msg-0\", \"reason\": \"High impact message - keep in context\", \"tokenSavings\": 0, \"impact\": \"high\" },\n    { \"type\": \"keep\", \"messageId\": \"msg-1\", \"reason\": \"High impact message - keep in context\", \"tokenSavings\": 0, \"impact\": \"high\" }\n  ],\n  \"attentionDistribution\": {\n    \"systemPrompt\": 0.98,\n    \"recentMessages\": 0.4,\n    \"olderMessages\": 0.2,\n    \"toolResponses\": 0\n  },\n  \"keyMessages\": [\n    { \"id\": \"msg-0\", \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"...\", \"impactScore\": 98 },\n    { \"id\": \"msg-1\", \"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"[]\", \"impactScore\": 96 }\n  ],\n  \"contextHealth\": {\n    \"score\": 80,\n    \"issues\": [\"System prompt takes up too much context\"],\n    \"recommendations\": [\"Consider shortening or optimizing system prompt\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 4) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/session\n\n按 `sessionId` 返回会话级统计与分析。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `sessionId`（必填）\n\n错误：\n- `400`: 缺少 `sessionId`\n- `404`: 找不到会话分析\n\n## 5) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/links\n\n返回主/子任务（subagent）关联边列表（spawn/send/ended）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `parentRunId`（可选）\n- `childRunId`（可选）\n- `parentSessionId`（可选）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应结构：\n- `links`: `SubagentLinkData[]`\n- `total`: 当前返回条数\n- `filters`\n\n## 6) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/tool-calls\n\n返回工具调用 span 列表（来自 `after_tool_call` 采集）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（可选）\n- `sessionId`（可选）\n- `toolName`（可选）\n- `startTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `endTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应（实时数据，limit=5）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"toolCalls\": [\n    {\n      \"runId\": \"0c28e5e1-581e-42df-ad47-2ba40aa1c8c2\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"2accf470-a410-405c-ad91-2d1cb497176d\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"toolName\": \"exec\",\n      \"toolCallId\": \"call_c492ff7dab2a4dbb9fb00ffc\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773159778376,\n      \"startedAt\": 1773159777837,\n      \"durationMs\": 539,\n      \"params\": {\n        \"command\": \"Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \\\"http://127.0.0.1:18789/plugins/contextscope/api/analysis?runId=4a2ae89b-3d65-4466-8ed1-11c7c01e394e\\\" -UseBasicParsing | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Content\"\n      },\n      \"result\": {\n        \"content\": [...],\n        \"details\": {\n          \"status\": \"completed\",\n          \"exitCode\": 0,\n          \"durationMs\": 545\n        }\n      },\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"runId\": \"0c28e5e1-581e-42df-ad47-2ba40aa1c8c2\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"2accf470-a410-405c-ad91-2d1cb497176d\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"toolName\": \"exec\",\n      \"toolCallId\": \"call_a65f17f69f6440ecb106921f\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773159772954,\n      \"startedAt\": 1773159772533,\n      \"durationMs\": 421,\n      \"params\": {\n        \"command\": \"Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \\\"http://127.0.0.1:18789/plugins/contextscope/api/requests?limit=5\\\" -UseBasicParsing | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Content\"\n      },\n      \"result\": { ... },\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 4\n    },\n    {\n      \"runId\": \"0c28e5e1-581e-42df-ad47-2ba40aa1c8c2\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"2accf470-a410-405c-ad91-2d1cb497176d\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"toolName\": \"exec\",\n      \"toolCallId\": \"call_78ee5ebdff8e44a89ec820e5\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773159767357,\n      \"startedAt\": 1773159766881,\n      \"durationMs\": 476,\n      \"params\": {\n        \"command\": \"Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \\\"http://127.0.0.1:18789/plugins/contextscope/api/stats\\\" -UseBasicParsing | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Content\"\n      },\n      \"result\": { ... },\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 3\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"filters\": {\n    \"limit\": 5,\n    \"offset\": 0\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 7) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/export\n\n导出请求事件数据。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `format`（可选，`json` | `csv`，默认 `json`）\n- `startTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `endTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `provider`（可选）\n- `model`（可选）\n\n响应：\n- `format=json`: `application/json`，内容为 `RequestData[]`\n- `format=csv`: `text/csv`\n\n## 8) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/timeline/detail\n\n返回某个 timeline point 的上下文快照。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n- `timestamp`（必填，毫秒时间戳；通常取自 `/api/analysis` 的 `timeline.points[].timestamp`）\n\n响应（示例）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": 1773158963814,\n  \"tokens\": 6863,\n  \"messages\": 1,\n  \"utilization\": 0.209,\n  \"summaryApplied\": false,\n  \"contextSnapshot\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"msg-0\",\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"[Wed 2026-03-11 00:09 GMT+8] 测试一下 ok\",\n      \"tokens\": 17,\n      \"timestamp\": 1773158963814,\n      \"type\": \"input\",\n      \"status\": \"success\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 9) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/timeline/compare\n\n对比两个 timeline point 的差异。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n- `timestamp1`（必填）\n- `timestamp2`（必填）\n\n响应（示例）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp1\": 1773158963814,\n  \"timestamp2\": 1773158975235,\n  \"messagesDelta\": 1,\n  \"tokensDelta\": 0,\n  \"utilizationDelta\": 0,\n  \"addedMessages\": [\n    { \"id\": \"msg-1\", \"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"ok\", \"tokens\": 1 }\n  ],\n  \"removedMessages\": []\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**数据采集时间**: Wed 2026-03-11 00:22 GMT+8  \n**服务状态**: 运行中  \n**总请求数**: 45  \n**存储大小**: 13.1 MB\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773159785631}}
