{"type":"message","id":"947a3e52","parentId":"a45e62ac","timestamp":"2026-03-10T16:32:41.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求查看最终统计数据并更新 API 文档，我需要先获取最新的 stats、links、tool-calls 和 requests 数据，然后用这些真实数据更新文档。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我获取最终统计数据并更新文档。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_93bb88da297e443686f5a2a2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"D:\\code\\request-analyzer\\API_DOC.zh-CN.md","content":"# ContextScope HTTP API 接口文档\n\nBase URL（默认）：`http://127.0.0.1:18789`\n\n插件路径前缀：\n- Dashboard：`/plugins/contextscope`\n- API：`/plugins/contextscope/api/*`\n\n示例数据（本机联调，实时数据）：\n- `runId`: `d43888a1-d47d-4402-97fe-ad582d8b1450` (主会话)\n- `sessionId`: `2accf470-a410-405c-ad91-2d1cb497176d`\n\n## 1) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/stats\n\n返回总体统计、存储统计与前端展示配置。\n\nQuery 参数：无\n\n响应（**实时数据 - 多 agent 测试后**）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"totalRequests\": 69,\n    \"todayRequests\": 29,\n    \"weekRequests\": 69,\n    \"averageTokens\": 0,\n    \"totalCost\": 0,\n    \"byProvider\": {\n      \"bailian\": 61,\n      \"openrouter\": 2,\n      \"anthropic\": 6\n    },\n    \"byModel\": {\n      \"qwen3.5-plus\": 61,\n      \"anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet\": 2,\n      \"claude-opus-4-6\": 6\n    },\n    \"hourlyDistribution\": [29, 0, 6, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 18, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 10]\n  },\n  \"storage\": {\n    \"totalRequests\": 69,\n    \"todayRequests\": 29,\n    \"weekRequests\": 69,\n    \"storageSize\": \"18.4 MB\",\n    \"oldestRequest\": 1773081035652,\n    \"newestRequest\": 1773160240634\n  },\n  \"config\": {\n    \"theme\": \"dark\",\n    \"autoRefresh\": true,\n    \"refreshInterval\": 5000\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 2) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/requests\n\n按过滤条件返回 LLM 请求/响应事件列表。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `sessionId`（可选）\n- `runId`（可选）\n- `provider`（可选）\n- `model`（可选）\n- `startTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `endTime`（可选，毫秒时间戳）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应结构：\n- `requests`: `RequestData[]`\n- `total`: 当前返回条数\n- `filters`: 实际生效的过滤条件\n\n## 3) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/analysis\n\n按 `runId` 返回聚合分析结果（token breakdown、timeline、insights 等）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n\n错误：\n- `400`: 缺少 `runId`\n- `404`: 找不到对应 `runId`\n\n## 4) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/session\n\n按 `sessionId` 返回会话级统计与分析。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `sessionId`（必填）\n\n## 5) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/links\n\n返回主/子任务（subagent）关联边列表（spawn/send/ended）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `parentRunId`（可选）\n- `childRunId`（可选）\n- `parentSessionId`（可选）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应（**实时数据 - 5 个子 agent 测试**）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"links\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"spawn\",\n      \"parentRunId\": \"d43888a1-d47d-4402-97fe-ad582d8b1450\",\n      \"childRunId\": \"97e40f43-6fab-4eec-a005-3365c659f444\",\n      \"parentSessionId\": \"2accf470-a410-405c-ad91-2d1cb497176d\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:837950ff-abf3-430b-a50d-166d58677c1e\",\n      \"runtime\": \"subagent\",\n      \"mode\": \"run\",\n      \"toolCallId\": \"call_60f8699638014350934e1bee\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773160060751,\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"spawn\",\n      \"parentRunId\": \"d43888a1-d47d-4402-97fe-ad582d8b1450\",\n      \"childRunId\": \"17bd3df0-c3d6-4c13-a24c-12f2831684aa\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:9c036b78-14b0-4038-a2b3-9920b6fbd2e8\",\n      \"runtime\": \"subagent\",\n      \"mode\": \"run\",\n      \"outcome\": \"success\",\n      \"endedAt\": 1773160079402,\n      \"id\": 4\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"spawn\",\n      \"parentRunId\": \"d43888a1-d47d-4402-97fe-ad582d8b1450\",\n      \"childRunId\": \"d30be165-ce30-4176-87e6-2789e7351308\",\n      \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:f7e9ca4c-262c-476f-a252-a8dc71d756ac\",\n      \"runtime\": \"subagent\",\n      \"mode\": \"run\",\n      \"outcome\": \"success\",\n      \"endedAt\": 1773160098284,\n      \"id\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"spawn\",\n      \"parentRunId\": \"d43888a1-d47d-4402-97fe-ad582d8b1450\",\n      \"childRunId\": \"d9fb5801-eb4b-40f9-83b4-290330b572a8\",\n      \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:fbae7b89-32ee-41d9-a888-8a7ab241fbc1\",\n      \"outcome\": \"success\",\n      \"endedAt\": 1773160033750,\n      \"id\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"spawn\",\n      \"parentRunId\": \"d43888a1-d47d-4402-97fe-ad582d8b1450\",\n      \"childRunId\": \"03ac5510-4382-4c21-adbc-990bd26288eb\",\n      \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:629cb399-5cce-43a5-a58a-55cfe9d4b9cd\",\n      \"outcome\": \"success\",\n      \"endedAt\": 1773160074964,\n      \"id\": 1\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"filters\": { \"limit\": 20, \"offset\": 0 }\n}\n```\n\n## 6) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/tool-calls\n\n返回工具调用 span 列表（来自 `after_tool_call` 采集）。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（可选）\n- `sessionId`（可选）\n- `toolName`（可选）\n- `startTime`（可选）\n- `endTime`（可选）\n- `limit`（可选，默认 100）\n- `offset`（可选，默认 0）\n\n响应示例（**实时数据 - 多 agent 测试**）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"toolCalls\": [\n    {\n      \"runId\": \"d30be165-ce30-4176-87e6-2789e7351308\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"32cea602-a935-4faf-9375-6a88dd689d7c\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:f7e9ca4c-262c-476f-a252-a8dc71d756ac\",\n      \"toolName\": \"exec\",\n      \"toolCallId\": \"call_ff5cda0834104402afd3dae2\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1773160032311,\n      \"startedAt\": 1773160030754,\n      \"durationMs\": 1557,\n      \"params\": {\n        \"command\": \"Get-CimInstance Win32_OperatingSystem | Select-Object TotalVisibleMemorySize, FreePhysicalMemory...\"\n      },\n      \"result\": {\n        \"content\": [{ \"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"TotalMemoryGB: 15.79, FreeMemoryGB: 2.38\" }],\n        \"details\": { \"status\": \"completed\", \"exitCode\": 0, \"durationMs\": 1808 }\n      },\n      \"metadata\": { \"agentId\": \"main\" },\n      \"id\": 42\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 30,\n  \"filters\": { \"limit\": 30, \"offset\": 0 }\n}\n```\n\n## 7) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/export\n\n导出请求事件数据。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `format`（可选，`json` | `csv`，默认 `json`）\n- `startTime`（可选）\n- `endTime`（可选）\n- `provider`（可选）\n- `model`（可选）\n\n响应：\n- `format=json`: `application/json`，内容为 `RequestData[]`\n- `format=csv`: `text/csv`\n\n## 8) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/timeline/detail\n\n返回某个 timeline point 的上下文快照。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n- `timestamp`（必填，毫秒时间戳）\n\n## 9) GET /plugins/contextscope/api/timeline/compare\n\n对比两个 timeline point 的差异。\n\nQuery 参数：\n- `runId`（必填）\n- `timestamp1`（必填）\n- `timestamp2`（必填）\n\n---\n\n## 📊 多 Agent 测试总结\n\n**测试场景**: 同时启动 5 个子 agent 执行不同任务\n\n| Agent | 任务 | Run ID | 状态 |\n|-------|------|--------|------|\n| code-analyzer-1 | 代码分析 | `03ac5510-4382-4c21-adbc-990bd26288eb` | ✅ 成功 |\n| research-agent-1 | 网络搜索研究 | `d9fb5801-eb4b-40f9-83b4-290330b572a8` | ✅ 成功 |\n| health-check-1 | 系统诊断 | `d30be165-ce30-4176-87e6-2789e7351308` | ✅ 成功 |\n| config-analyzer | 配置分析 | `17bd3df0-c3d6-4c13-a24c-12f2831684aa` | ✅ 成功 |\n| tech-researcher | 技术栈调研 | `97e40f43-6fab-4eec-a005-3365c659f444` | ✅ 成功 |\n\n**测试结果**:\n- 总请求数：69 次（测试前 45 次 → 测试后 69 次）\n- 新增请求：24 次\n- 存储大小：18.4 MB\n- 工具调用：30+ 次\n- 子 agent 关联：5 条 spawn 记录，全部成功完成\n\n**数据采集时间**: Wed 2026-03-11 00:30 GMT+8  \n**服务状态**: ✅ 运行中  \n**测试状态**: ✅ 所有子 agent 完成\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773160249826}}
